text: Libyan Canadians () are Canadians of Libyan descent . Most Libyan Canadians speak Arabic, English or French. According to the 2011 Census there were 5,515 Canadians who claimed Libyan ancestry. ==See also== * Arab Canadians * Libyan Americans == References == == External links == * Category:Arab Canadian Canadian Category:African Canadian
title: Libyan Canadians
